snippet.title: Tchia - PlayStation Showcase 2021: Tropical Adventure Trailer | PS5, PS4
snippet.description: A Tropical Open-World adventure. Climb, glide, swim, and sail your boat around a beautiful archipelago in this physics-driven sandbox. Use Tchia's Soul Jumping ability to take control of any animal or object you can find, and Jam on your fully playable Ukulele. A game inspired by New Caledonia.
